snippet.textDisplay: That Riley, boy! I'm really grooving on his style! I've complained about the humor on the regular TechLinked segments before, but here it seems like it's more natural. So now I'm thinking that it's either just the way the regular segments are edited or maybe it's just that the ratio of jokes to information is too high. I try to figure in the fact that maybe I'm just an old curmudgeon who is losing his sense of humor as he ages, but I don't really think I'm _that_ alone in this regard. I don't know. Just throwing it out there. But anyway, Riley is spot on in the humor and information delivery. He can joke for a bit, but he's really good at dialing it back down and getting and keeping things on track. He's definitely a keeper! So please make sure to keep his water and food bowls full and his bedding washed regularly. He deserves it! ;) :P
